Sentencas: Ultrathin 3 mol.% yttria-stabilised-tetragonal-zirconia-polycrystal (Y-TZP) foils with thicknesses of 1-10 mu m are fabricated by a new wet-chemical processing route.
Titulo: Micro-solid oxide fuel cells using free-standing 3 mol.% yttria-stabilised-tetragonal-zirconia-polycrystal electrolyte foils

Sentencas: The foils are free-standing, semi-transparent and flexible.
Titulo: Micro-solid oxide fuel cells using free-standing 3 mol.% yttria-stabilised-tetragonal-zirconia-polycrystal electrolyte foils

Sentencas: The in-plane electrical conductivity of the Y-TZP foil is 0.03 S m(-1) at 500 degrees C. Cross-plane impedance measurements with sputtered Pt electrodes yield two arcs, of which the high-frequency arc is attributed to the ohmic resistance of the electrolyte and the low-frequency arc to the electrode-electrolyte interface.
Titulo: Micro-solid oxide fuel cells using free-standing 3 mol.% yttria-stabilised-tetragonal-zirconia-polycrystal electrolyte foils

Sentencas: A symmetrical micro-solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) is designed using this ultrathin free-standing Y-TZP foil as the electrolyte and sputtered Pt electrodes.
Titulo: Micro-solid oxide fuel cells using free-standing 3 mol.% yttria-stabilised-tetragonal-zirconia-polycrystal electrolyte foils

Sentencas: An open-circuit voltage of 0.98V and a maximum power density of 12 mW cm(-2) are measured at 500 degrees C.
Titulo: Micro-solid oxide fuel cells using free-standing 3 mol.% yttria-stabilised-tetragonal-zirconia-polycrystal electrolyte foils

Sentencas: These results prove the feasibility of this approach to the fabrication of miniaturised planar SOFCs without the need for microfabrication.
Titulo: Micro-solid oxide fuel cells using free-standing 3 mol.% yttria-stabilised-tetragonal-zirconia-polycrystal electrolyte foils
